headline: Palo Alto Networks' Stock Has Tanked But Its FCF is Strong - Price Target is 15% Higher
summary: Palo Alto Networks' stock is well off its highs, despite producing stellar free cash flow and FCF margins for its fiscal Q1 ending Oct. 31. That implies its price target is at least 15% higher at $212 per share.
